title: County Business Patterns, Jobs by Sector (1km Grid), USA NE Corridor, 1994-2003
name: County Business Patterns, Jobs by Sector (1km Grid), USA NE Corridor, 1994-2003
description: This dataset contains estimates of the number of jobs per zip code based employment center in 1994 and 2003.  It was generated as follows; (1) Using 1994 and 2003 data from the US Census Bureau's County Business Patterns series, zipcode-based job counts were estimated for every 4-digit SIC and NAICs industry group by applying a series of mid-point estimates to an establishment size frequency distribution; (2) The resulting job counts were summarized by major sector; (3) The resulting sectoral totals were geocoded to their zipcode locations; (4)  Job totals in ipcode centroids and points within 500 meters of each other were aggregated together to form unique job centers.
